@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Terms of Service";
}

<div class="container mt-5 pb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h1 class="fw-bold display-5 mb-3">Terms of <span style="color: var(--accent);">Service</span></h1>
                <p class="text-muted lead">Last updated: April 2026</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-card shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5 mb-4" style="background-color: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;">

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">1. Acceptance of Terms</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    By accessing and using AssetInsight, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you are prohibited from using our platform. These terms govern your use of our financial tracking tools, algorithmic backtesting engine, and social features.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">2. Accounts and External Logins</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    To access certain features, you must create an account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials.
                </p>
                <div class="alert alert-dark border-secondary mb-4" style="background-color: var(--bg-main);">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill text-success me-2"></i><strong>External Authentication Promise:</strong> When you choose to register or log in using third-party external providers (such as <strong>Google, Microsoft, or Facebook</strong>), we enforce strict data minimization. The <strong>only</strong> data we request, access, and store from these external providers is your <strong>Email Address</strong> and <strong>Name</strong>. We do not—and will never—access your contacts, personal files, browsing history, or any other private data associated with your external accounts.
                </div>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">3. No Financial Advice</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    AssetInsight is exclusively an educational, analytical, and simulated environment. <strong>We do not provide financial, investment, or legal advice.</strong> The algorithmic backtesting results, market news, and community posts provided on this platform are for informational purposes only. Historical performance of any trading strategy evaluated in our Backtest Engine is not indicative of future results. You assume full responsibility for any real-world trades or investments you make.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">4. User Content and Conduct</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    Our platform allows users to create custom trading strategies, post content, and interact with others. By using these features, you agree not to:
                </p>
                <ul class="text-muted mb-4">
                    <li class="mb-2">Post spam, malicious links, or misleading financial schemes (e.g., "pump and dump" promotions).</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Harass, abuse, or harm other users in the comment sections or community feeds.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Attempt to reverse-engineer, overload, or disrupt the AssetInsight Backtest Engine or APIs.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these community guidelines without prior notice.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">5. Intellectual Property</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    The AssetInsight platform, including its original code, backtest engine architecture, and visual design, is owned by us and is protected by copyright and intellectual property laws. However, any custom trading strategies or personal posts you create remain your intellectual property.
                </p>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 border-bottom border-secondary pb-2">6. Limitation of Liability</h4>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                    In no event shall AssetInsight, its developers, or its affiliates be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages, including but not limited to loss of capital, profits, or data, arising out of the use or inability to use our platform or the reliance on any data provided by our third-party integrations (such as Finnhub).
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>